\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And because of that it seems to make sense that we should spend time focusing on this topic but far too often we don\'92t\'85we don\'92t like to think about it\'85we don\'92t like to discuss it\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t know if there is a more important topic and yet it is often relegated to the sidelines of our thought lives for what are perceived as more important and relevant issues to today\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What I think happens is we have an enemy, a spiritual enemy, and his job is to get us to look down at our feet\'85I think he does even better by having us look backward at what we have done/not done (which is the antithesis of \'93looking forward\'94)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}To look down and just right now and not worry about what happens next\'85because if he can get you to look down\'85well so goes not just your body but in this case\'85your soul!\
