\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Did you catch that\'85that tension of where they were looking and in turn what they were doing.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Peter essentially says to:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Keep your eyes on heaven, and your feet on the ground.   \
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Old adage of \'93keep your eyes on the prize\'94\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}I believe this is how we are called to live our lives but often we don\'92t.\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}And I think we don\'92t because we don\'92t know what heaven even looks like\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}Hollywood has done an incredible job of creating a dull false version of heaven that even I think isn\'92t worth looking forward to\'85and especially not worth sacrficing for...\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You will never 
\f0\b SACRIFICE
\f1\b0  for what you can not 
\f0\b SEE
\f1\b0 \
