\ls6\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}This is why so much of the Christian faith doens't make sense for so many who show up week in and week out...\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You want good words from me\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You want advice on how to make this life better\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}You want to figure out how to get God on your side to make THIS life better\
